snippet.title: Breakwaters - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Breakwaters is currently in Early Access on Steam !

Join us for some fun exploration adventure with the largest ocean simulation ever in a game.  ... did I mention the Titans?  There are Giant creatures roaming the world which you can fight!

Get the game here and join the community:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1203180/Breakwaters/
